GroovePHP - A PHP wrapper for the APIShark Grooveshark API.
========================================================
_By Ben Kulbertis_

Licensing
---------
GroovePHP is released under the [**GNU General Public License, version 2**](http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html)

APIShark
--------
[APIShark](http://apishark.com) is a public API for the popular music steaming service _Grooveshark_ written by [James Hartig](http://about.me/jameshartig).
You need an API key (which are freely available if you have a grooveshark account) to use the API. Please read the [API Terms of Service](http://apishark.com/API_TOS.pdf) before using the API.